> LOOK UP MANDRAKE IN HERBAL
(first taking Aelred's Herbal)
Mandrake: called the sleeping root. In small doses brings drowsiness and eases pain. A large root consumed or its smoke deeply breathed brings profound sleep, useful before surgery or for serious insomnia. Not dangerous to handle, but it should not be eaten.

